{"word":"σίζω","slug":"σίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n94087\" key=\"si/zw\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">σίζω</orth>, mostly used in <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ pres.\">pres.</a></tns> and <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ impf.\">impf.</a></tns>: <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\">aor. 1</tns> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σίξα</foreign> prob. in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0005.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:29\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Theoc.\">Theoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.29</biblScope> </bibl>:—<sense id=\"n94087.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">hiss</tr_>, esp. of the noise made by plunging hot metal into cold water, to which is compared the hissing of the Cyclops' eye when the burnt stake was thrust into it, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὣς τοῦ σίζ᾽ ὀφθαλμὸς ἐλαϊνέῳ περὶ μοχλῷ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:9:394\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.394</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; so of pancakes, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0474.tlg001:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Magn.\">Magn.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τάγηνον σίζον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg002.perseus-grc1:930\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eq.\">Eq.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">930</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; of fish frying, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1158\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ach.\">Ach.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1158</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Com.Adesp.\">Com.Adesp.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">140</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ς. καὶ ψοφεῖν</foreign>, of fire quenched, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg001:94b:33\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ APo.\">APo.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">94b33</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σίζει δὲ ταῖς ῥίνεσσι κινεῖ δ᾽ οὔατα</foreign>, of Heracles snorting as he eats, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0521.tlg001:21\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Epich.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21</biblScope> </bibl>; of the note of the <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κόψιχος</foreign>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:5:89\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Poll.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.89</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}